gobblin.source.extractor.extract.kafka.workunit.packer

Class KafkaWorkUnitPacker

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.source.extractor.extract.kafka.workunit.packer.KafkaWorkUnitPacker
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    KafkaBiLevelWorkUnitPacker, KafkaSingleLevelWorkUnitPacker

    public abstract class KafkaWorkUnitPacker
extends Object
    An abstract class for packing Kafka WorkUnits into MultiWorkUnits based on the number of containers.
